          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1916.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>quick cook amorini </strong>to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the amorini for just 2-3 min (it will keep cooking in the sauce later!)</p><p>Once done, drain the amorini, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
