    {
      "instruction": "<p>Carefully peel the skin off the <strong>salmon</strong> and discard </p><p>Break the <strong>salmon</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces with a wooden spoon, then add the <strong>pesto</strong> and <strong>soft</strong> <strong>cheese</strong> with 75ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span><strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and stir it all together</p><p>Cook for 1 min further or until the sauce has thickened slightly</p>",
